Login system according to: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-RCnNyD0L-s

INSTALATION PROCESS:
npm init
npm i express ejs
npm i --save-dev nodemon dotenv

npm i bcrypt
npm i passport passport-local express-session express-flash
In case of TROUBLE with SESSION restart server and clear data in browser

npm run devstart

npm i method-override // logout





EXPRESS SERVER SKELETON:
const express = require('express');

const app = express();
app.listen(3000);



EXPRESS SERVER showing SIMPLE PAGE:

const express = require('express');
const app = express();
app.set('view-engine', 'ejs'); //set view engine to ejs ~ when use ejs only ~

app.get('/', (req, res) => {
  res.render('index.ejs');
});
app.listen(3000);
